com.xatkit.plugins.discord.platform.io

Class PrivateMessageListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dv8tion.jda.core.hooks.ListenerAdapter
      • com.xatkit.plugins.discord.platform.io.PrivateMessageListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.dv8tion.jda.core.hooks.EventListener

    public class PrivateMessageListener
extends net.dv8tion.jda.core.hooks.ListenerAdapter
    A ListenerAdapter that listen private messages and send them to the underlying XatkitCore.

    This class is instantiated by its containing DiscordIntentProvider, and is used to react to Discord messages. Note that this listener only forwards not empty, not null messages to the XatkitCore, in order to avoid useless calls to the underlying DialogFlow API.

      • onPrivateMessageReceived

        public void onPrivateMessageReceived(net.dv8tion.jda.core.events.message.priv.PrivateMessageReceivedEvent event)
        Handles the received private message event and forward it to the XatkitCore.

        Empty and null messages are filtered in order to avoid useless calls to the underlying DialogFlow API. In addition, messages send by other bots are also ignored to avoid infinite discussion loops.

        Overrides:
        onPrivateMessageReceived in class net.dv8tion.jda.core.hooks.ListenerAdapter
        Parameters:
        event - the PrivateMessageReceivedEvent wrapping the received message
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if the provided event is null
